#: urpm/cli/main.py:597
msgid ""
"Create a minimal Mageia Docker/Podman image for RPM builds.\n"
"\n"
"The image contains a minimal system with urpm configured to use\n"
"the official Mageia mirrors. Use with 'urpm build' for isolated builds.\n"
"\n"
"Profiles are loaded from:\n"
"  /usr/share/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (system)\n"
"  /etc/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (local additions)\n"
"\n"
"Examples:\n"
"  urpm image make --release 10 --tag mageia:10-build\n"
"  urpm image make -r 10 -t mga10-build --buildrequires SPECS/foo.spec\n"
"  urpm image make -r cauldron -t mga-cauldron --profile ci\n"
msgstr ""
"Crea un'immagine Docker/Podman Mageia minimale per la compilazione di RPM.\n"
"\n"
"L'immagine contiene un sistema minimale con urpm configurato per utilizzare\n"
"i mirror ufficiali di Mageia. Da utilizzare con 'urpm build' per compilazioni isolate.\n"
"\n"
"I profili vengono caricati da:\n"
"  /usr/share/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (di sistema)\n"
"  /etc/urpm/profiles/*.yaml (aggiunte locali)\n"
"\n"
"Esempi:\n"
"  urpm image make --release 10 --tag mageia:10-build\n"
"  urpm image make -r 10 -t mga10-build --buildrequires SPECS/foo.spec\n"
"  urpm image make -r cauldron -t mga-cauldron --profile ci\n"

